<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">

    <title>Grégory Lefebvre | Développeur Full-Stack Ruby on Rails</title>
